Usage: AWAYENCR on|off
  Toggles encryption of ScrollZ.away on/off

  If ON, the ScrollZ.away log file will be encrypted using
  master password as a crypt key. When OFF, the ScrollZ.away
  log file will not be encrypted. The encrypted log file can
  be decrypted using a tool called SZdecode found in tools
  subdirectory in the ScrollZ source archive.

See also:
  AWAYT
  PLAYBACK
  REMLOG
  SETAWAY
  SETBACK
  SHOWAWAY
